="_ _6"></span>实际上是汉族</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y40 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">人，<span class="_ _5"></span>具体是什么年代呢？应该是唐朝初年。<span class="_ _5"></span>他曾去印度依止</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y41 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">了蒋华西宁，<span class="_ _6"></span>得到大圆满的窍诀，<span class="_ _6"></span>此后又返回汉地，<span class="_ _6"></span>住于清</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y42 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">凉尸陀林</div><div class="t m0 xc he y189 ffc fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9</div><div class="t m0 x51 h4 y42 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">。 </div><div class="t m0 x1f h4 y60 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls5a ws0">当时，在印度某个城市中，布玛莫扎和嘉纳思札<span class="fs4 ls5b">（益西</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h11 y18a ffc fs4 fc0 sc0 ls5c ws0">多）</div><div class="t m0 x29 h4 y61 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls5d ws0">共同学习五明。一天，他们二<span class="ls5e">人去金刚座旁的一个花园</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y46 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls19 ws0">散步</div><div class="t m0 x25 h21 y19 ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">埵</div><div class="t m0 x1f h4 y46 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls14 ws0">，突见金刚萨<span class="_ _1d"> </span>在空中授记：<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls12">“你们虽曾五百世转为班</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y47 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">智达，<span class="_ _6"></span>却尚未获得果位。<span class="_ _6"></span>若想即生解脱，<span class="_ _6"></span>应前往汉地清凉尸</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y48 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls19 ws0">陀林。<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls14">”听到此话，布玛莫扎立即<span class="ls12">动身去汉地，依止了西日</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h6 y49 ff7 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">                                        <span class="_ _2"></span>               <span class="_ _5"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x9 hf y4a ff7 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9</div><div class="t m0 x22 h10 y4b ff7 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">  <span class="ffd">清凉尸陀林，据说在现在的五台山那边。</span> </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
